Package: rustkube-node
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Glenn West <glennswest@neuralcloudcomputing.com>
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Depends: iproute2
Description: RustKube node components (kubelet, kube-proxy)
 Drop-in Kubernetes node components in Rust from the rustkube project:
 kubelet (node agent; CRI v1 over gRPC to CRI-O/containerd) and kube-proxy
 (iptables service dataplane). Uses exact upstream names and config paths
 under /etc/kubernetes.
